title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Nov 18 2021

description:
Identity politics and cancel culture will ultimately destroy the Democrat Party. Exhibit A: Joy (Everything-Is-Racist) Reid. Clay and Buck long for a conservative city. Why the definition of fully vaccinated is going to change. Wisconsin Senator Ron Johnson on Kamala Harris, Rittenhouse trial, and whether or not he might run for re-election.
